* Unix
******

1. Compile library

  make
  make byte    # if you only want bytecode compilation
  make opt     # if you only want native code compilation

2. Example program

  make ex

3. Installation

  Installation requires ocamlfind.

  make install

4. Documentation

  make doc


* Windows
*********

Typing "make" will compile the library and demonstration program to
bytecode .

It will only work if you get a ANSI compatible terminal.
POINTERS NEEDED.